Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 這裏是它的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青鬼蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:34.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲奉行大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.12,0:01:40.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於邀請津輕藩的劍術教頭月島源十郎作為蟲奉行所的同心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人似乎已經無法行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:46.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取而代之前來的 是其公子月島仁兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:51.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願他對江戶安泰能有所貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:59.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【對手是女忍者 火缽】
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.98,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這裏是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.05,0:02:08.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無…無涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:18.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會成為戰無不勝至死方休的強大武士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.28,0:02:31.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個糟糕的噩夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:34.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:39.16,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天爺 今天也請多多指教!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:42.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島仁兵衛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:44.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.26,0:02:53.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛大人 要努力工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:05.17,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 清晨的修煉 揮刀練習3000遍 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:09.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今日起 終於要開始在蟲奉行所的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 請您看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:16.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我月島仁兵衛一定會出色地履行職務
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:21.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定不辜負江戶人們和蟲奉行所的同伴們的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:23.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 無涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.84,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了回報您的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:33.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更為了能不斷向您靠近 在下一定會變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:38.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一大早就這麼倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 火缽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到早會的時間了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:48.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~不好意思 您在換衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在下就先行一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次來的新人 一大早就精神充沛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:12.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正很快就會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:27.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛君 你的傷勢如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.75,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖您的福 已經痊癒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:31.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:37.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 無涯大人 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無 無…無涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:48.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然全員都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:57.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  首先向仁兵衛君說明一下這裏的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:58.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:04.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過昨日那一戰 我想你已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:09.67,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這日本盤踞著可以吞食人類的巨蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:13.76,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從迄今100年前起便開始肆意橫行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:19.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於它們從何而來 又是為何出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現今仍在調查中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 在下以前遇到的就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕就是蟲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:31.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過仁兵衛君的故鄉津輕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:34.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及奧州那一帶或許是由於氣候寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本不應有蟲棲息才對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:44.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而於10年前 為保護江戶民眾免受巨蟲襲擊而設立的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:46.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這所新中町奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.43,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又稱蟲奉行所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:54.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在蟲奉行大人手下 每日從事驅除蟲子的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:58.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位蟲奉行大人現在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必讓在下與他見上一面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:03.30,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那個必要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:08.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲奉行大人從不在人前露面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:12.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人是不可能見得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:14.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就連我們也從沒見過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:15.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:19.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 仁兵衛君 明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:23.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上 承擔著守護江戶太平的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:31.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙如此信任 身為武士者已了無遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:39.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我月島仁兵衛  定會出色完成朝廷所賜的這一職務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉身碎骨 在所不辭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:46.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣身為保護江戶之人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下定不負各位的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:57.37,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大 大事不好 松之原大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟲子出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:00.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:04.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是從立川往西去了 具體行蹤還…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:06.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大家分頭搜查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:09.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:15.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 仁兵衛君 你暫時在一旁看著學習就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必參與戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:25.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下 為何不讓在下參加戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:29.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也是蟲奉行所的一員啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:35.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說嗎 顯然是因為你很弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:41.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪打正著讓你打倒了一隻蜘蛛 可能有些沾沾自喜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:45.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裏  可沒有一個人對小哥你抱有期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有家可歸的話還是回家比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連 連無涯大人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:02.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這一年裏進入蟲奉行所的新人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:07.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到十天就全部在工作中死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:12.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經沒有繼續物色人才的精力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:18.06,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此仁兵衛君在這一個月之內禁止拔刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:20.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是身為與力的我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹…謹遵命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:33.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 為什麼偏偏要跟你分到一組啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:41.30,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:45.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下在想無涯大人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對在下來說 無涯大人就是夜空中閃耀的星辰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:52.61,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他深深吸引了在下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:57.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也崇拜著無涯大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也 是什麼意思 火缽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:09.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 火缽小姐也跟我一樣崇拜著無涯大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:14.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可比你崇拜他的多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.91,0:09:16.83,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 火缽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.83,0:09:19.93,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無涯大人到底是怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.66,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴在下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:31.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無涯大人呢 總之就是無人能及的使劍高手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  除此之外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有傳言說他在來蟲奉行所之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:42.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一個叫「蟲狩」的組織裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.70,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「蟲狩」？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.08,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個強者雲集的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是接受委託 驅除蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:52.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際上誰也說不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過說到底 傳言始終是傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:59.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種神秘之處也是無涯大人的魅力所在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 真不愧是在下所崇拜的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:06.16,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了 是我更崇拜他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下也不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 無涯大人是真的很強
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:16.34,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說 他都曾救過在下的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:18.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也被救過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:21.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火缽小姐也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:25.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了 請務必將當時的事講給在下聽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你想聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:34.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一年前離開老家的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的故鄉是在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:40.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位於伊賀和甲賀交界處的忍者隱居之地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 既不是伊賀流也不是甲賀流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:46.04,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.29,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:55.80,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 在使用炸藥進行爆破方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:58.62,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們曾是首屈一指的忍術一族
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:05.27,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  到了太平盛世 就不再需要忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:09.98,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我小的時候 人們已經從事著普通的工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:16.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有曾是一族頭領的爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在深山裏繼續修行著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.90,0:11:23.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺子你也是時候該回村子裏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:27.78,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼修煉也沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:29.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今這世道 忍術還有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.55,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:42.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火缽 又到爺爺這兒來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:47.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  對孫女倒是疼愛的很
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:49.21,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只有在這點上 還算是個普通老人家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺你看 飯團炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.82,0:12:12.58,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得真好啊 小火缽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡爺爺了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是他那只有我能見到的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:26.49,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是窮其一生追求巔峰的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:32.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知何時 我也開始想要變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.02,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 幾年之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.18,0:12:44.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥大人聽聞村裏有個年輕的女忍者 特地遠道而來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要接受在蟲奉行所裏的職務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.97,0:12:57.42,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能在蟲奉行所裏嶄露頭角
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:13:00.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺的流派或許就能再次名揚世上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:09.98,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的流派是屬於男子的東西 只屬於男子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:13.03,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖教你 卻沒有讓你繼承它的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:22.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  我還是想守護爺爺窮其一生心血的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:28.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就決定到蟲奉行所任職
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:37.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後終於到了我初次執行任務的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:46.87,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無涯大人救了我一命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:54.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他面前 蟲子根本不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:02.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我便知道了在江戶 有真正的強者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:08.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望有一天 自己能強大到足以獲得無涯大人的認可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以報答他的救命之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的實力能增進到那種程度 一定能..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到 火缽小姐也和在下一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:17.72,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下在蒙無涯大人相救之時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切實體會到了父親所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了父親所說的 為了不讓身後的人為恐懼所吞沒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.47,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士絕不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:35.44,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無涯大人之強 足以驅散身後守護之人的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:44.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那一刻 在下就決定了要以無涯大人為前進的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.12,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無涯大人就是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:50.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人想要變成他那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:51.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.81,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:53.05,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:53.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:54.25,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:55.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:01.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要和你一起說無涯大人說得那麼興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:04.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別太得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:05.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火…火缽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:09.63,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:28.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.31,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 這裏是它的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.01,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青鬼蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:45.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是蜻蜓的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:49.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟鬼蜻蜓一樣 對於河畔附近的領地具有強烈的佔有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:54.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至日落黃昏 氣溫下降之時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.89,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會為了獵食而開始在空中飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:02.40,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不愧是火缽小姐 知道得真詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:07.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 因為這傢伙跟我在初次執行任務時遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同一種蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.03,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:14.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島 你把那兩人帶到遠處去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.86,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是 火缽小姐 您一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:19.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被命令不許拔劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:22.41,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:25.94,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我一定要一個人消滅這只蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.74,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.10,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 您一定要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來了 青鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:40.45,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次執行任務的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:44.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能站在無涯大人的身後發抖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:53.88,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在已經不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫陽花玉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.32,0:17:05.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是那時的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止它 憑己之力消滅它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:13.15,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來證明我的改變
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:27.96,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:30.57,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火滅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:35.23,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:04.35,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無…無涯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.64,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事吧 火缽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.20,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月 月島
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:13.79,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經照您吩咐 將那兩人帶到安全之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.54,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.60,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:20.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的獵物 我自己來消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要由我一個人來消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.39,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能證明我變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.39,0:18:34.80,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無涯大人也一定會認同我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.68,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:38.24,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:47.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個職位並不是讓您用來證明自己強大的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.48,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無涯大人也一定是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.72,0:18:54.07,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火缽小姐您也是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:19:01.51,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你我 都是被無涯大人那一心只為戰而戰的身影所吸引的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還輪不到你來說我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:17.73,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上吧 月島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.46,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快把這傢伙收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:24.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:33.71,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常住戰陣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕技  小太刀千花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:08.14,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火缽小姐 水溫怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:10.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不夠熱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:11.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:21.53,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛君 你拔劍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.35,0:20:23.33,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:26.52,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 月島沒有拔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:30.26,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有從劍鞘裏拔出來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 火缽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:32.77,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您今天火藥爆破的招數也非常精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.39,0:20:38.99,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼流派的招數啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.69,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會告訴別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:44.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.22,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.13,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.19,0:20:51.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.90,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍寶流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.65,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍 珍寶流嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.82,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲 聲音太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:03.92,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:12.28,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個 死色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.56,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係變好些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.11,0:23:02.11,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍術的秘訣在於蒟蒻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:02.97,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒟蒻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.97,0:23:04.95,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 現在就開始特訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.95,0:23:08.32,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春小姐 請將你那兩個「蒟蒻」球借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.32,0:23:09.85,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁兵衛大人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.96,0:23:11.50,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 蟲奉行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.50,0:23:14.19,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九十九人斬 戀川春菊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,mushibugyo_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
