Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.92,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:23.65,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了令人憂傷的純粹簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:26.97,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在夕陽西下時的道場一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:29.65,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}揮灑著汗水練習刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.98,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.64,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了引人發笑的滿腔熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.02,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「我也是有夢想的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.99,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像傻瓜般這樣大聲叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:46.34,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.63,0:00:49.18,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝陽東昇的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.25,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你會在喧鬧的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:55.08,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拚命奔跑著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:58.27,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.16,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}深夜降臨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.35,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你會穿過寬闊的大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:06.22,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在河灘邊訴說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:09.34,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是這樣吧 我的摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.49,0:01:16.61,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摯友啊 摯友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:19.37,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了一顆赤子之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.71,0:01:22.53,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你正守護著重要的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.46,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}臉上透露著決心吧
